Went here for a birthday party. Kids had TONS of fun. My kid is on the smaller side, but he was able to climb almost all of the inflatables. We didn't know there was an actual snow room or we would've brought a coat and boots. Next time, we will bring them.

The staff was very friendly. The birthday rooms were small, but they fit our birthday party just fine. The pizzas for the party were 'catered' in from Mr. Jim's Pizza.

We will be back.}
